Structura
-src: server.py (entry point aplicatie)
      config.yaml (date conectare baza de date)
      helper.py (functii pentru request-uri, realizare conexiune baza de date, validare date si generare raspuns)
      requirements.txt 
      wait_for_db.sh (porneste serverul)
      Dockerfile
      .dockerignore
      
      api:
      CitiesApi: definire endpoint-uri cities
      CountriesApi: definire endpoint-uri countries
      TemperatureApi: definire endpoint-uri temperatures
      
      db:
      create_tables.sql: script de initializare baza de date

Rulare: docker compose up / docker compose -f docker-compose.yml up